Just mixed this up, based on the smell after a shake i'm giving this four stars - I'll update once I vape it after 10 days. This steep may kill me!&#xD;
&#xD;
*Update*  Here we are eleven days later.  I cracked it open at 9 days and the cake base was being bullied by the orange quite a bit.  After two more steeping days, I get cake and orange, but the cranberry seems a bit muted.  This may be that my sense of taste sucks after years of smoking, but I think that I'm going to bump up the amount of cranberry in my next mix to about 2.25%.
